KEYWORD: Drugs

DIGEST: Applicant failed to mitigate security concerns regarding drug involvement and substance misuse. His drug use continued after giving assurances that he would no longer use marijuana, and was subsequently granted a Secret security clearance. After being granted a clearance, he not only continued to use marijuana, but expanded his drug use to include cocaine, MDMA, lysergic acid diethylamide (LSD), prescription medication Hydrocodone, and prescription medication Adderall. Clearance is denied.

